text: "You Got What It Takes" is a 1959 song by Marv Johnson and it was taken from his album Marvelous Marv Johnson. It went to number 10 in the United States and number 5 in the United Kingdom. It was covered in 1967 by The Dave Clark Five and reached number 28 in the United Kingdom and number 7 in the United States. ==References== Category:1959 songs Category:R&B; songs Category:The Dave Clark Five songs
title: You Got What It Takes
